/amplify_video/2044097451167285248/vid/avc1/320x568/3BYFoLiAEYP47fQA.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2007190860690046977/ZAITQvgd_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Clown World \u2122 \ud83e\udd21", "username": "ClownWorld"}, "content": "This woman recorded her own parents and put them on social media for supporting Trump and ICE. Now she's shocked she's getting kicked out. Her political beliefs have turned her against her own family.  \n\n", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1685}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZQzbZQt", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8560557, "raw_content": "Conservative journalist Savanah Hernandez just thanked Vice President JD Vance for spotlighting the brutal assault she suffered at the hands of violent leftists in Minneapolis.\n\n\u201cNot only has the response from this administration been quick,\u201d she said, \u201cbut this is the first time I\u2019ve experienced the federal government actually utilize multiple agencies to hold these violent leftists responsible.\u201d\n\nShe continued: \u201cPreviously, attacks on journalists like myself would be completely ignored, but this administration immediately followed up with me and opened an investigation. I\u2019m extremely grateful and am looking forward to seeing the full force of the law utilized against these violent leftwing activists. Not only for me, but for all of my friends who have been assaulted before.\u201d\n\nThis is the sea change America voted for. Under Biden and the radical left, conservative journalists were fair game \u2014 beaten, doxxed, and ignored by federal agencies that treated Antifa and BLM rioters like protected activists.\n\nNow the Trump administration is treating leftwing political violence like the domestic terrorism it is. Multiple agencies, real investigations, and the full force of the law.\n\nNo more free passes for the mob. The message is loud and clear: assault patriots and you will face consequences.", "author": "JohnyBlaze99", "created": 1776267147632, "profile_picture": "ZzxODHntx36H", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "SAVANAH HERNANDEZ THANK JD VANCE: TRUMP ADMIN FINALLY USING FULL FEDERAL FORCE AGAINST VIOLENT LEFTIST THUGS", "last_comment_created": 1776267147631, "content": "<p>Conservative journalist Savanah Hernandez just thanked Vice President JD Vance for spotlighting the brutal assault she suffered at the hands of violent leftists in Minneapolis.</p>\n<p>\u201cNot only has the response from this administration been quick,\u201d she said, \u201cbut this is the first time I\u2019ve experienced the federal government actually utilize multiple agencies to hold these violent leftists responsible.\u201d</p>\n<p>She continued: \u201cPreviously, attacks on journalists like myself would be completely ignored, but this administration immediately followed up with me and opened an investigation. I\u2019m extremely grateful and am looking forward to seeing the full force of the law utilized against these violent leftwing activists. Not only for me, but for all of my friends who have been assaulted before.\u201d</p>\n<p>This is the sea change America voted for. Under Biden and the radical left, conservative journalists were fair game \u2014 beaten, doxxed, and ignored by federal agencies that treated Antifa and BLM rioters like protected activists.</p>\n<p>Now the Trump administration is treating leftwing political violence like the domestic terrorism it is. Multiple agencies,